Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is a complex issue and it is too difficult to categorize it as good or bad.  There are pros, such as making friends more easily, and living much closr to your classes, and there are cons.  Such as more frequent vandelization and students being sheltered from life experience in the real world.